ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: A code that identifies the kind of trait being asserted.

ivardefs.name: exclude
ivardefs.desc: If true, indicates the characteristic is one that is NOT held by members of the group.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: The period over which the characteristic is tested; e.g. the patient had an operation during the month of June.

properties.desc: Identifies the traits shared by members of the group.
